These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Job: firefighter, photographer, paramedic
1. Job:photographer is on the right of Job:paramedic##1
2. Job:firefighter is on the far right##1
3. Job:firefighter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Job   | paramedic | photographer | firefighter |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Pet: lizard, cat, guinea-pig
1. Pet:cat is in an odd position##4
2. Pet:lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Pet   | lizard | guinea-pig | cat |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Nationality: german, nigerian, american
1. Nationality:nigerian is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:nigerian is on the left or right of Nationality:american##3
3. Nationality:american is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Nationality   | german | nigerian | american |

 #################################
 
